## Language

- [You can now use the slice pattern syntax with subslices.](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/67712/) e.g.

  ``` rust
  fn foo(words: &[&str]) {
      match words {
          ["Hello", "World", "!", ..] => println!("Hello World!"),
          ["Foo", "Bar", ..] => println!("Baz"),
          rest => println!("{:?}", rest),
      }
  }
  ```

